Tyrael: What the maximals may lack in number, they make up in
strength. Even now, we do not match their number. I'll wait before
offering an alliance so Rodimus doesn't realize what happens. Now, if
you allow me, I'd like to have access to a lab computer. I have
precious data to store.

He pulled a small datachip from between two feathers and held it
between his fingers.
